<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Werner Neumeyr</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass sich der Adressat nicht an die Georg III. von Fraunberg zum Haag, Pfleger zu Schärding, zuliebe gewährte Frist gehalten hat, und verweist wegen Neumeyrs angeblichen Besitz zu Nürnberg auf den Rechtsweg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_424" id="211r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_424_r2l15">Wernhart Neẅmeyr </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><note place="marginleft"><ab facs="#facs_424_r1l3"><expan>ſ<ex>i</ex>n<ex>e</ex></expan> <expan>ſ<ex>er</ex>uico</expan> et </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_424_r1l4"><expan>ſalutac<ex>i</ex>o<ex>n</ex>e</expan> </ab></note>
<ab facs="#facs_424_r2l16">Wernhart Neẅmeyr als du vns yecʒ <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> haſt etc das haben </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_424_r2l17">wır <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> wır <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſchrıft pıllıch von dır <expan>v<ex>er</ex>tragen</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_424_r2l18">Vnd als <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> görg <expan>frawmberg<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒum Hag <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu Scherdıng </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_424_r2l19">von deinen <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> verd mıt vns redt vnd bat / dem ʒulıeb gaben </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_424_r2l21">wır dır ein frıſt . Darinn du wol ʒu vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_424_r2l20"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>eſt</expan> </ab></add> vnd dein ſache </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_424_r2l22"><expan>auſʒgetrag<ex>en</ex></expan> hettſt / des haſt du niht getan / Vnd als du meldſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_424_r2l23">von hab <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe du bey vns haben ſülleſt / Der <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir nıht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_424_r2l24">ynnen vnd <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> auch <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> niht / wıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> deẅht dıch daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_424_r2l25">keinr der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> . hab bey vns Jnnenhett / dıe dein pıllıcher <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_424_r2l26">ſo macht du <expan>dein<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ſcheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mıt <expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan> vollen gwalt <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_424_r2l27">wol ʒu vns ſchıken / dem wellen wir <expan>freẅntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> vor </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_425" id="211v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_425_r1l1">des Reıchs <expan>Rıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> bey vns ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> . wenn wır des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_425_r1l2">ermant <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> . ſo <expan>dıeſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ʒu den du ʒuſprechen hettſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_425_r1l3">anheim bey vns ſeyn on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſ<ex>ub</ex></expan> ſıgıllo Petrȷ <expan>volkm<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_425_r1l4"><expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>iſt</ex>rıciuiu<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> Judıca </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_424" id="211r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Wernhart Newmeyr</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab><app>
<note place="marginleft">
<expan>S<ex>i</ex>n<ex>e</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>er</ex>vico</expan> et <expan>salutac<ex>i</ex>o<ex>n</ex>e</expan>.
              </note>
</app>Wernhart Newmeyr, als du uns yecz <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hast etc.,
            das haben wir <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> wir
                <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> schrift pillich von dir
              <expan>v<ex>er</ex>tragen</expan>; und als <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Görg
                <expan>Frawmberg<ex>er</ex></expan> zum Hag, <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> zu
            Scherding, von deinen <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> verd mit uns redt und bat, dem
            zulieb gaben wir dir ein frist, darinn du wol zu uns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><expan>w<ex>er</ex>est</expan></add> und dein sache
              <expan>auszgetrag<ex>en</ex></expan> hettst, des hast du niht getan; und als du meldst
            von hab <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die du bey uns haben süllest, der
                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir niht ynnen und <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> auch
                <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> niht. Wie <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> dewht dich
            daz keinr der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hab bey uns innenhett, die dein pillicher
                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, so macht du <expan>dein<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>scheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan> vollen gwalt
                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wol zu uns schiken, dem wellen wir
                <expan>frewntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> vor <pb facs="#facs_425" id="211v"/>des reichs
                <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan>, wenn wir des ermant <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, so
                <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan> die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, zu den du
            zusprechen hettst, anheim bey uns seyn on <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>.
                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>ub</ex></expan> sigillo Petri <expan>Volkm<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>ist</ex>ri</expan>
<expan>civiu<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> judica. </ab></div>
</div></body>
